data.description: Welcome to 11542 Wayne Carreon Street, a charming and inviting home nestled in a sought-after neighborhood. This beautifully maintained 3 bed, 2 bath bath residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting living area. The kitchen is a focal point, boasting center island, ample storage,  quality appliances, and a dining space. The master's bedroom is a serene retreat featuring a walk-in closet, a bathtub and a separate bathroom plus a double vanity sink. Outside, the backyard is an oasis for relaxation or gatherings, featuring a covered patio. Don't miss this opportunity to own a delightful home in a fantastic location!
